tafsir[2]{c,v,t}:
  11,121,"(And say unto those who believe not) in Allah and the Last Day nor in the revealed Scriptures and prophets: (Act according to your power) in your dwellings act according to your religion so as to destroy me. (Lo! we (too) are acting) to destroy you."
  11,122,"(And wait) for my destruction! (Lo! we (too) are waiting) for your destruction."